title: Trendscendentalism 1/25: Harriet Tubman, 0% ICU, Dominion, Godzilla vs King Kong

description:
On this edition of Trendscendentalism Jack and Miles discuss the Biden admin putting Harriet Tubman on the $20 bill, there are literally no hospital beds free in LA as Gavin Newsom lifts "Stay At Home" restrictions, Dominion is suing Rudy Giuliani for his attacks during the Presidential race, and the Godzilla v King Kong trailer has the internet talking and meming.
